-- 0000_init.sql: scaffold; no entities yet. See plan §4 for v1 entities.
-- Phase 0.2 (cards 0.9 / 0.10 / 0.11) adds operational / lot / compliance tables.
--
-- This file is a self-documenting marker for the migration history. Drizzle-kit
-- does NOT emit a SQL migration for an empty schema (verified in card 0.4 —
-- `pnpm db:generate` against an empty src/schema/index.ts reports
-- "No schema changes, nothing to migrate"). The first REAL migration will be
-- generated by card 0.9 when the operational schema lands, at which point
-- drizzle-kit will create 0001_<name>.sql + the journal entry pointing to it.
--
-- This placeholder is committed (not gitignored) so the migration directory is
-- present and the history has a documented starting line. It contains no DDL
-- and is never executed by `drizzle-kit migrate` because it is not referenced
-- from meta/_journal.json.
